                        <h3>Touch a rock</h3>
                        <p>To give the participating pre-service teachers an insight into the program rock specimens from the Museum collection were handed out and each participant was asked to look at the rock, describe it and express what they thought the story of the rock might be.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
