            <section>    
                <h2>Challenges?</h2>

                <p>As with any program of this nature, there were also some challenges. In particular, scheduling and timetabling was particularly difficult, due to variations in study periods at Deakin University and the University of Melbourne. In 2016, the program will be delivered separately to pre-service teachers from Deakin University and the University of Melbourne, to avoid to scheduling difficulties.</p>
            </section>
