        <div class="two-thirds">
            <section>
                <h2>Impact – success</h2>

                <p>Despite the challenges, feedback from the participants was very positive; pre-service teachers appreciated the rare opportunity to increase their knowledge of the geology and produce engaging teaching resources for Level 8 Earth Science curriculum.</p>

